stock.model

Class RegularStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • stock.model.RegularStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Strategy

    public class RegularStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
implements Strategy
    A Strategy class that implements a regular investment strategy of buying one stock at a given amount on a given day. It takes a commission parameter which will be factored in the cost basis of the stock. Allows to add stocks only on business day and time.
